<div class="content-wrap">
  <header class="home-header">
    <div class="home-header-left">
      <div class="home-header-logo">
        <svg width="50" height="50" viewBox="0 0 50 50" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="25" cy="25" r="23" fill="#ff6b00"/>
          <text x="25" y="35" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="30" font-weight="bold" fill="black" text-anchor="middle">R</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1>RAYPE</h1>
    </div>
    <nav class="home-nav">
      <span class="home-nav-btn home-nav-user">
        <%= current_user.email %>
        <% if current_user.admin? %>
          <span class="home-user-badge">ADMIN</span>
        <% end %>
      </span>
      <a href="#" class="home-nav-btn">Ajuda</a>
      <a href="#contact-section" class="home-nav-btn" id="contact-button">Contato</a>
      <a href="#services-section" class="home-nav-btn">Orçamentos</a>
      <% if current_user.admin? %>
        <a href="/sidekiq" target="_blank" class="home-nav-btn">Sidekiq</a>
        <a href="/flipper" target="_blank" class="home-nav-btn">Flipper</a>
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to "Sair", destroy_user_session_path, data: { turbo_method: :delete }, class: "home-nav-btn btn-logout" %>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <div class="home-banner">
    <div class="home-banner-carousel" id="carousel-container">
      <div class="home-banner-slide" id="home-slide-1">
        <h1>SLIDE 1: OUTDOOR TRIEDO</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="home-banner-slide" id="home-slide-2">
        <h1>SLIDE 2: OUTDOOR TRIEDO</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="home-banner-slide" id="home-slide-3">
        <h1>SLIDE 3: NOVIDADE LED</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="home-description">
    <h1 class="home-description-title">Bem Vindo à Raype!</h1>
    <p class="home-description-text">
      Na Raype, atuamos no ramo de marketing com outdoors triedo e outdoors de LED, mas o que realmente nos diferencia
      são as nossas ideias inovadoras e o compromisso em oferecer outdoors de verdade. Saia do comum. Venha para a Raype
      e descubra como podemos transformar a maneira como o seu público vê a sua marca.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="home-services" id="services-section">
    <h1 class="home-services-title">Orçamentos</h1>

    <div class="home-services-grid">
      <div class="home-service-card">
        <i class="home-service-icon fas fa-map-location-dot"></i>
        <div class="home-service-description">Qual outdoor?</div>
        <button class="home-service-btn">Escolher</button>
      </div>

      <div class="home-service-card">
        <i class="home-service-icon fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
        <div class="home-service-description">Qual Data?</div>
        <button class="home-service-btn">Escolher</button>
      </div>

      <div class="home-service-card">
        <i class="home-service-icon fas fa-signs-post"></i>
        <div class="home-service-description">Escolha sua Arte?</div>
        <button class="home-service-btn">Escolher</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<footer class="home-footer" id="contact-section">
  <div class="home-footer-content">
    <p>Siga-nos nas Redes Sociais:</p>
    <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/R.+Heitor+Ferrari+Hablich,+189+-+Centro,+Dois+Vizinhos+-+PR,+85660-000/@-25.7469195,-53.053471,17z"
       target="_blank"
       class="home-social-link">
      <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
      Instagram Raype
    </a>
    <p class="home-copyright">&copy; 2026 RAYPE - Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

